2015年9月20日，未来小子释出了与加拿大嘻哈艺人德雷克合作的混音带——《What a Time to Be Alive》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2015/09/20/drake-future-what-a-time-to-be-alive-mixtape/|title=Stream Drake and Future’s Mixtape ‘What a Time to Be Alive’|accessdate=2015-09-30|work=Rap-Up|archive-date=2015-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928094524/http://www.rap-up.com/2015/09/20/drake-future-what-a-time-to-be-alive-mixtape/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/what-a-time-to-be-alive/id1041818504|title=What a Time To Be Alive|accessdate=2015-10-19|work=iTunes|archive-date=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016225114/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/what-a-time-to-be-alive/id1041818504|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这张专辑成为了自2004年Jay Z以来的十一年中，首张同时在公告牌二百强专辑榜、公告牌R&B榜单和公告牌说唱榜单上取得冠军的专辑。 混音带在美国已经售出超过334,000份。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2015/09/28/drake-future-what-a-time-to-be-alive-debuts-at-no-1/|title=Drake and Future’s ‘What a Time to Be Alive’ Debuts at No. 1|accessdate=2015-09-30|work=Rap-Up|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929203905/http://www.rap-up.com/2015/09/28/drake-future-what-a-time-to-be-alive-debuts-at-no-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2016年1月17日，未来小子释出了另一张混音带——《Purple Reign》，专辑由[[Metro_Boomin|Metro Boomin]]和DJ Esco监制，并与Southside、Zaytroven等艺人合作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/62966-future-drops-purple-reign/|title=Future Drops Purple Reign|language=en-US|website=Pitchfork|access-date=2016-02-01|archive-date=2016-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129102239/http://pitchfork.com/news/62966-future-drops-purple-reign/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2016年2月5日，未来小子在DJ 哈立德主持的新一期Beats 1广播节目《We The Best》上释出了他的第四张录音室专辑——《EVOL》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2016/02/01/dj-khaled-to-premiere-new-future-album/|title=Future to Premiere New Album on DJ Khaled's Radio Show|accessdate=2016-07-01|publisher=|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611041256/http://www.rap-up.com/2016/02/01/dj-khaled-to-premiere-new-future-album/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在2016年，未来小子成为自2010年《欢乐合唱团》原声带以来，在最短时间内拥有三张美国公告牌二百强专辑榜冠军专辑的歌手。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uproxx.com/music/evol-future-number-one-billboard-glee/|title=The Success Of 'EVOL' Puts Future In The Same Company As 'Glee'|language=en-GB|website=UPROXX|access-date=2016-02-19|archive-date=2016-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219101013/http://uproxx.com/music/evol-future-number-one-billboard-glee/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年6月9日，未来小子登上《滚石》杂志。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thefader.com/2016/06/29/future-rolling-stone-cover-ciara|title=Future Covers Rolling Stone|last=McCormick|first=Luke|date=2016-06-29|newspaper=[[The_Fader|The Fader.com]]|location=Music|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701125137/http://www.thefader.com/2016/06/29/future-rolling-stone-cover-ciara|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2017年-至今: <span>Future</span> ===
2017年[[情人节|情人节]]，未来小子在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上宣布，他的第五张录音室专辑，即同名专辑，将于2017年2月17日释出。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/future/id1205691905|title=Future by Future|accessdate=2017-02-14|date=2017-02-14|work=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]]|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306154348/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/future/id1205691905|dead-url=no}}</ref> 一个星期之后，他将释出自己的第六张录音室专辑——《HNDRXX》。2018年1月，他客串美國創作歌手[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]的歌曲「[[游戏终结|End Game]]」，並獲得許多佳績及獲得[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]的白金認證。

== 音乐风格 ==
未来小子经常在自己的歌曲——无论是说唱还是演唱部分——使用[[Auto-Tune|Auto-Tune]]。《[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]]》评论道，未来小子“出人意料的向我们展示了，Auto-Tune仍可以作为一件艺术工具”，并称他“找到了许多使用该软件去增强和修饰情感的方式”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/16554-pluto/|title=Future: Pluto Album Review - Pitchfork|accessdate=2016-07-01|publisher=|archive-date=2013-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117020118/http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/16554-pluto/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 《[[GQ|GQ》]]称，他“设法赋予了令人生厌的Auto-Tune新的能力"，表示他"将它与低吟相结合，以表达他的情感，然后[...]延伸和修饰他的歌词，直到他们不太像日常的语言，而是更像即将喷薄而出的情感”。 《<span>[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉矶时报》]]</span>写道，“未来小子高度处理的人声描绘出了一个为爱情、毒品或科技推向迷茫和绝望的男人的形象”，并称他的音乐“奇迹般的表现了对时间的麻木”。<ref name="Latimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-future-hollywood-palladium-review-20160319-story.html|title=Future reflects the overstimulation of our time -- or he's just busy|accessdate=2016-08-25|last1=Wood|first1=Mickael|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-date=2016-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828145559/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-future-hollywood-palladium-review-20160319-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年，同样使用音频处理器的嘻哈歌手[[T-Pain|T-Pain]]，批评了未来小子的对其的非传统使用。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bet.com/news/music/2013/02/14/t-pain-future-is-not-using-auto-tune-correctly.html|title=T-Pain: Future Is Not Using Auto-Tune Correctly|accessdate=2015-04-22|date=2013-02-14|last=Reagans|first=Dan|publisher=BET|archive-date=2015-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707114544/http://www.bet.com/news/music/2013/02/14/t-pain-future-is-not-using-auto-tune-correctly.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 对此，未来小子在接受采访时表示，“从我第一次使用Auto-Tune开始，我从来不用它来歌唱。 我不像T-Pain那样使用它。我用它来说唱，因为它能使我的声音更具有标志性。 现在大家都想使用Auto-Tune。我并不代表所有人。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.complex.com/music/2013/01/future-my-complex-interview|title=My Complex: Future Talks Auto-Tune, Dumbing Down Music, and Why He's Not a Romantic|accessdate=2015-04-22|date=2013-01-23|publisher=Complex|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708132359/http://www.complex.com/music/2013/01/future-my-complex-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>未来小子的音乐风格被人们称为[[陷阱音樂|陷阱音乐]].<ref name="dj-mag">{{cite web|url=http://djmag.com/content/trap-music-under-lock-key|title=The trap phenomenon explained|accessdate=2013-05-30|publisher=[[DJ_Magazine|DJ Mag]]|archive-date=2013-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723021444/http://djmag.com/content/trap-music-under-lock-key|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
未来小子与Jessica Smith、Brittni Mealy、India J和歌手[[席亞拉|席亚拉]]四个女人结过婚，并各有一个孩子。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2014/01/14/future-four-children-ciara-baby-mama-drama/|title=Future's Four Children — Ciara's Baby Daddy Has Kids With Different Women – Hollywood Life|accessdate=2015-10-19|author=Hollywood Life Staff|work=Hollywood Life|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006052138/http://hollywoodlife.com/2014/01/14/future-four-children-ciara-baby-mama-drama/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，他在2013年10月与席亚拉结婚，但2014年8月，席亚拉与其断绝了关系。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ciara-calls-off-engagement-to-future-after-he-cheated-2014138|title=New Mom Ciara Calls Off Engagement to Future After Rapper Cheats|accessdate=2016-07-01|publisher=|archive-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618223604/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ciara-calls-off-engagement-to-future-after-he-cheated-2014138|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他们的儿子Future Zahir Wilburn，出生于2014年5月19日。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.eonline.com/news/694959/ciara-gushes-over-son-future-1-and-talks-about-challenge-of-her-russell-wilson-s-no-sex-policy-watch|title=Ciara Gushes Over Son Future, 2, and Talks About Challenge of Her & Russell Wilson's No-Sex Policy: Watch! – E! Online|accessdate=2015-10-19|date=2015-09-11|work=E! Online}}</ref>

